title: Chris Christian Discography 1984-1999 (6 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
CHRIS CHRISTIAN DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 6 releases...

 * 1984 - Let The Music Start
 * 1988 - No Lyrics
 * 1991 - Higher Ways
 * 1991 - Sketches
 * 1995 - The Producer
 * 1999 - Essential Hits

Chris Christian born in Abilene, Texas, is a songwriter, record producer, and a record label executive. His songs have been recorded by Elvis Presley, Olivia Newton-John, Natalie Cole, Sheena Easton, The Pointer Sisters, Al Jarreau, The Carpenters, Amy Grant, Patti Austin, Dionne Warwick, America, The Imperials, B.J. Thomas, B W Stevenson, Marilyn McCoo, Dan Peek, Cheryl Ladd, Jane Olivor, Sandi Patti, Ali Lohan, Donnie and Marie Osmond, and others.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - December 2014
